flowchart TD
    A[Airflow schedules run] --> B[Ingestion fetches and publishes]
    B --> C[Kafka topic]
    C --> D[Bronze bounded batch]
    D --> E{Any valid transformed rows?}
    E -- No --> S1[Skip write and end run]
    E -- Yes --> F[Deduplicate by event_id]
    F --> G[Write Bronze parquet]
    G --> H[Persist next offsets.json]
    H --> I[Run Silver]
    I --> J[Run Gold]
    J --> K[Run Platinum stage job]
    K --> L{Stage table valid?}
    L -- No --> X1[Validation failure]
    L -- Yes --> M[Merge stage into target]
    M --> N{Post-merge validations pass?}
    N -- No --> X2[Validation failure]
    N -- Yes --> O[Successful run]

    P[Backfill queue in ops.backfill_jobs] --> Q[Claim next chunk]
    Q --> A
    X1 --> R[Mark backfill failed if applicable]
    X2 --> R
    R --> T{Stale or retryable later?}
    T -- Yes --> U[Recover stale job and retry up to cap]
    T -- No --> V[Manual investigation]

    W[Dormant Bronze verification/repair path]
    W -. coverage scan .-> Y[ops.bronze_hourly_coverage]
    Y -. missing hours can enqueue .-> Z[ops.bronze_repair_jobs]
